19-07-31T17:30:38.000Z","msg":"沒有暴徒，只有暴政！"},{"pid":"651b331ccec2bbc55670a44ffd9cdfbf6cbd496e","tid":1392400,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:31:15.000Z","msg":"元朗恐襲 放生石鏡泉何君堯已經係黑暗中既黑暗<br />\n無普選高官可以為所欲為<br />\n垃圾會保皇黨功能組別又盲撐政府<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以解決根源問題係普選<br />\n香港有超強籌碼爭取普選<br />\n目前要重點爭取 <strong>獨立調查員會+普選</strong></span><br />\n聽吓呢個分柝<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IngG2ukLCBU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIngG2ukLCBU&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGIICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=6a61c0d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IngG2ukLCBU</a>"},{"pid":"aa6224b6bcf4a47372a56480064a8dba5ede64a9","tid":1392400,"uid":199902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e64d70a7683297ac71089712a2913d4a25f413c0","tid":1392400,"uid":31719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ba76bd54fa31ca1a4dde657583baaa34aee5694","tid":1392400,"uid":31719,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:29:30.000Z","msg":"屌戇撚鳩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:29:48.000Z","msg":"回錯post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:31:38.000Z","msg":"回錯就幫推啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"588fbeff5a1ee344a03becb589f26ad8538d65df","tid":1392400,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:35:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5900a0728c08f78f33024ec291ff25a6ffe8df4f","tid":1392400,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2